    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290960/extras/ede1bfa19b1699cb6b9da3da0b25e880.avif?t=1704479980\" width=616 height=120 /></span><br><br><strong>Z 特工的新任务是在卡兰国家。 完美的情报人员 Z 已准备好竭尽全力摧毁您控制下的目标犯罪组织。</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290960/extras/f2f2aebc841a0e00cbbc733be541ad0c.poster.avif?t=1704479980\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290960/extras/f2f2aebc841a0e00cbbc733be541ad0c.webm?t=1704479980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290960/extras/f2f2aebc841a0e00cbbc733be541ad0c.mp4?t=1704479980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要任务</h2><strong>犯罪组织已经接管了卡兰地区几乎所有的工厂。 这个犯罪组织的头目Atilla Tartan的主要目标是控制卡兰，他几乎成功了。 作为 Z 特工，阻止它并清理 Atilla 造成的混乱</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290960/extras/4186f442456a0db915ae033789b30af0.poster.avif?t=1704479980\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290960/extras/4186f442456a0db915ae033789b30af0.webm?t=1704479980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290960/extras/4186f442456a0db915ae033789b30af0.mp4?t=1704479980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎来到卡兰</h2><strong>卡兰是一个岛国，面积 85 平方公里，由 9 个地区组成。 上路探索未受破坏的森林、发展中的城市、以野生动物而闻名的荒地，以及保留其传统结构的城镇。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290960/extras/d996f78f57676e8b3680b29ce5e73d2d.poster.avif?t=1704479980\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290960/extras/d996f78f57676e8b3680b29ce5e73d2d.webm?t=1704479980\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2290960/extras/d996f78f57676e8b3680b29ce5e73d2d.mp4?t=1704479980\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的开放世界</h2>你可以在开放世界中进行许多活动，例如驾驶改装汽车赛车、执行货物运输任务、使用拖拉机进行农活、射击场的各种瞄准挑战、在森林和荒地中寻宝等等。</strong>",
